					"type": 23,
					"value": "ReCon (commands must be done in this order):\n\r\n- SetGlobalOsirisFlag DEN_ShadowDruid_State_SnakeCourtStarted\r\n- \nloadlevel SCL_Main_A\n\r\n- addTag ACT2_SHADOW_CURSE_IMMUNE:b47643e0-583c-4808-b108-f6d3b605b0a9  (so we don't die of shadowcurse)\r\n\n- goto -150; 31; 18\r\n\n\nThen talk to Arabella"
				},
