				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player comes upon a familiar face in the cursed land: Arabella, the girl they rescued from the snake in act 1. She has developed powers and is rooting shadow-creatures. She promises you to teach you this entangling power if you save her parents, who are lost."
				}
